Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========OP===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:07.81,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 我能说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:10.98,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感触是否能传达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:13.55,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:15.45,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意爱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.46,0:00:21.01,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取得爱的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:33.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你的手所拥在怀里 在耳边轻声细语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:47.89,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远都不要离开我 我会给你个甜美的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:52.92,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请感受我 请了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:56.97,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我揽在你的臂弯里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.71,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你对我轻轻地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:04.13,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将日日夜夜爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:09.86,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人比我更爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:13.08,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爱是如此真诚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:15.29,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:17.42,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否爱我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:22.75,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们取得爱的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:37.12,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱走被炉猫！无论如何要暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您会看上那被炉 可见您是个行家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想隐瞒 可是只要看背影就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经那样看了1个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 那被炉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便宜卖你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是从高贵的住家所让予的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百元如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(「刀片」与「买」同音)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 买了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何…这次该我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0胜120负啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是120胜0负
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道拉姆姐是120胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是以那呆子的立场说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,120场连败呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通人是办不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是120连胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道拉姆姐是120连胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是以那呆子的立场说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一起来取笑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啊 达令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负还未定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第121负
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！被炉动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无法相信 被炉会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炉动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令赖皮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然偏离话题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是说这种话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把眼睁大看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炉是活的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我赢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么被炉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不想被盖上被子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪症
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吵 到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸虾沾上灰怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿当 听不见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧 太太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫僧来了就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸虾都由我保护了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从您儿子房间散发出一股妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.85,0:06:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为尽快将妖气去除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才如此跑来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么直接到阿当房间去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思议的被炉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然讨厌被盖被子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怕热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是通灵者说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么…一股炸虾的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我赢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,121负啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦人啊 小鬼天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空压顶成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冷风
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该和这呆子被炉断绝关系比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何就此罢手\N身为被炉业余专家的自尊无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对无聊的东西搞什么自尊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意志真是棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 有章鱼的家纹在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 章鱼之纹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说是面堂家的被炉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去问持有人最快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 马上叫他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂混球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0.1秒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看 面堂家的情报网
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有听你说话的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:08:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼力还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这被炉曾是面堂家所有的珍品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昵称小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原料是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南极一棵杉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南极一棵杉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如其名是南极中只长一棵的杉木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因在极寒之地长大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极端讨厌热之因果的被炉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法之下脱手了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来 是你买了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这原本是面堂家的东西所以贵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炉爱好者第一人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:10:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎那封闭之心或许可以开启
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.35,0:10:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你对被炉的爱与信念之下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是世界上最固执的被炉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会静静地顽石点头的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这之后有什么样的苦难等着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对世间的不了解 毁谤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.93,0:10:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使一片嘲笑之声来临…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是面堂家没一人办到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你却办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把麻烦推掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小太郎已经毫无关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别得意 你这铜臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有替小太郎想过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因为他不听话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就轻易脱手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事后一副事不关己的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为有你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以校内暴力才不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么 摸不着头绪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 我还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你试试看能否为他盖上被子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了 如果这样你能同意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么行为 小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为被炉还如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩 斩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的首级砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这被炉真是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎在那儿等着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看来是普通的横木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让看得人心里头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予安详的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即沿0.352486的弯曲度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微的和鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚不粗不细
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而横木与横木间的接点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已被禁止之尾羽波式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以第三段交接
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出于名人之手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎之生父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是具有制作被炉二百年历史的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一师相傅的名门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲蟹家的后人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲蟹之佐吉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子有必要造访那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐吉在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐吉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是破旧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真脏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的住在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫佐吉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没搬家才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来造访我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 佐吉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.99,0:14:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这大叔？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做那个被炉的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了我终太郎了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终太郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧 耳朵好像有些重听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是面堂终太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 原来是面堂的少爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能住在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来请教有关小太郎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是南极被炉的小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然记得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎是我一生一世的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但生来背负着不幸的被炉也非常稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐吉 为何不看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中计了 中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子们中奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐吉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为被炉还笑 什么家伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说什么少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请将小太郎变成正常的被炉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果太刺激小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被小太郎灵气所控制
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本全国的被炉将会叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炉叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点儿也没有危机感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可小看被炉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能再被炉上打麻将
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃卤豆腐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且更加恐怖的是冬天里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先将内衣放在被炉下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此期间取暖之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庶民的乐趣也将被夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子演得好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炉怎么会有灵性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是能熬的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炉猫有没有好招数
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不良被炉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那小太郎也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他生来就讨厌热的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才请你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将小太郎做成普通的被炉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是小太郎会希望如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要那么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管那个被炉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你自己一人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有在听 被炉猫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这被炉是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那被炉即使是你也无法驾驭的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个有阴暗人生的被炉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不讲义气的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西给我被卡车撞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后破坏的乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就最爽…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会跑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是葱太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉只有那么一点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是猪肉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 还号称什么甲蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把这两个人考虑进去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 有没有鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不留点儿给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到就立直了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 把这么多被炉弄成如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了 是小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点儿捉到他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的晚餐毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是被炉 和野狗一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎已非纯讨厌热的被炉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那些冰冻的被炉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在寻找同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 他必定找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该发觉自己的孤独了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小太郎需要的是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被炉的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是被炉之爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 这富有魅力的线条
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用三棵阿拉斯加松树\N打造而成的本人的究极作品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炉阿松
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.90,0:21:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 不做点什么的话小太郎会散架的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这渣被炉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就把你撕成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.27,0:21:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就只有一张被炉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭都还未吃叫我怎办 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做挡箭牌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太郎 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的 被炉猫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐吉 你来这里干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打救小太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以毒攻毒 被炉问题还要被炉来解决
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张被炉是什么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用三棵阿拉斯加松树打造而成的被炉阿松
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炉阿松…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一闪一闪的在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.43,0:22:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用被炉语在交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炉语？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊 拉姆姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.78,0:23:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.13,0:23:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是传说中的被炉彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来谣传是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.06,0:23:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在过去众多传说中\N没有比这更加奇妙美丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许某天他们俩\N还会出现在我们眼前也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介的父亲有一段不为人知的罗曼史
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.50,0:23:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓天意弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在晦涩的记忆中重现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:24:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史上最强伤感演出
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.92,0:24:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.67,0:24:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介之父纯情啊！\N妻子的身影在回忆中！！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.74,0:24:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:30.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将银轮偷偷交给你 这是只有你一人的邀请函
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.31,0:24:36.01,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我尝试保有它 是我小小的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.01,0:24:41.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定在今日 只有两人的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.79,0:24:49.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是公开的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.77,0:24:53.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将准备庆贺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.65,0:24:56.62,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！宝贝 给你个讯息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.35,0:25:00.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将献上所有的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.34,0:25:04.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.31,0:25:08.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你早些感受我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.23,0:25:12.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来！给我些诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.99,0:25:16.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要我如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.07,0:25:19.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请常来看我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.69,0:25:22.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将表示我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.86,0:25:27.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我和你在一起时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.50,0:25:30.67,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是如何的美好

